```bash
Java Side                     JNI Bridge                    C++ Side
──────────                     ──────────                    ────────
   jdouble                         |                     meters_t Object
   (double)                        |                           |
     |                             |                           |
     |      [ JNI Conversion ]     |                           |
     |----------------------------&gt;|                           |
     |                             |    Construct meters_t     |
     |                             |  using jdouble value      |
